===Specifications=== *ADSL/ADSL2+/VDSL/VDSL2+ compatible *Dual-band concurrent Wi-Fi interfaces: :802.11n 2.4GHz (2x2), 802.11ac 5GHz (3x3) *Ports: 1x WAN GbE, 2x FE LAN, 2x USB 2.0 *Built-in DLNA allows for media sharing (USB) *DECT and VoIP capabilities *Telstra Air compatible
